title: Tonka On The Job [English] [PC]
description:
Category: PC - KIDS GAME
Language: English
Type:Simulation
Quality: CD
Format: BIN-CUE
Size: 745.13 MB



Youre on the job and theres work to be done! Control the toughest trucks on the planet to build foundations dig canals clear trees and more. Build haul and demolish your way through each job! Use 13 of the toughest Tonka vehicles including Toughest Mighty Mighty Cement Mixer Tough Trencher Tough Bulldozer Helicopter and more! Test your construction and destruction skills in dirt yards cities gravel pits and more! Save the day putting out yard fires rescuing injured workers and hauling vehicles out the crews way. Prove you can get it done in Job Mode where real-life construction projects will test you to the limit or roam free in Free Play Mode.
